OL,3,CDisabled man left to eat from bin: ITV
OL,4,CNews exposes 'appalling' neglect
OL,6,FDisabled people are being neglected in
OL,7,Fhomes run by one of the UK's largest
OL,8,Fprivate care companies, with one
OL,9,Fvulnerable resident filmed eating out
OL,10,Fof a bin and another left with an
OL,11,Funtreated infection causing his foot
OL,12,Fto rot, as ITV News Investigations
OL,13,FEditor Dan Hewitt reports.
OL,15,FAdditional reporting by ITV News
OL,16,FSenior Producer Isabel Alderson-Blench
