OL,3,CDisabled man left to eat from bin: ITV
OL,4,CNews exposes 'appalling' neglect
OL,6,FIn one home in Coventry, camera
OL,7,Ffootage obtained by ITV News shows a
OL,8,Fyoung man with learning disabilities,
OL,9,Fautism and bipolar disorder, who needs
OL,10,F24-hour, one-on-one care, eating out
OL,11,Fof a rubbish bin in the middle of the
OL,12,Fnight.
OL,14,FIn another Lifeways home in North
OL,15,FLondon, I was told how the foot of a
OL,16,Fman with Down's Syndrome turned black,
OL,17,Fafter an infection was left undetected
OL,18,Fand untreated for weeks, causing him
OL,19,Fto require hospital treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/33
