OL,6,FLifeways is a private company which
OL,7,Foperates in England, Scotland and
OL,8,FWales, contracted by local authorities
OL,9,Fto provide care for more than 4,000
OL,10,Fpeople with complex conditions
OL,11,Fincluding learning disabilities,
OL,12,Fautism, acquired brain injuries, and
OL,13,Fmental health conditions.
