OL,6,FYet several families, as well as
OL,7,Fformer and current staff members, have
OL,8,Ftold ITV News that they believe
OL,9,FLifeways is consistently putting
OL,10,Fprofits before the people it is paid
OL,11,Fto care for, including people with
OL,12,Flearning disabilities who are unable
OL,13,Fto communicate and advocate for
OL,14,Fthemselves.
OL,16,FLast year, Lindsay Foskett reached out
OL,17,Fto ITV News about the treatment of her
OL,18,Fson Connor at a Lifeways-run facility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/33
