OL,6,FConnor is 23 and has a rare genetic
OL,7,Fcondition called Phelan-McDermid
OL,8,FSyndrome, which causes developmental
OL,9,Fdelay and autism. He also has bipolar
OL,10,Fdisorder.
OL,12,FIn 2018 Connor was placed under the
OL,13,Fcare of a Lifeways-run residential
OL,14,Fhome in Coventry. The city council
OL,15,Fcontracted Lifeways to provide Connor
OL,16,Fwith 24-hour, one-to-one care at a
OL,17,Fcost of #4,700 a week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/33
