OL,6,FHowever, two years ago, Lindsay
OL,7,Fstarted to worry about her son's
OL,8,Fphysical and mental health after he
OL,9,Fgained seven stone in weight.
OL,11,FHe was barely leaving the facility,
OL,12,Fdespite the council paying for
OL,13,Fextensive activities in the community.
OL,14,FHis mood was also deteriorating.
OL,16,FOne afternoon Lindsay got a phone call
OL,17,Ffrom a friend saying she had found
OL,18,FConnor walking the streets, several
OL,19,Fmiles from his home, on his own.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/33
