OL,6,FWhen Lindsay called Lifeways, she says
OL,7,Fstaff did not even know he had gone
OL,8,Fmissing, despite being paid to provide
OL,9,Fround the clock care.
OL,11,FIncreasingly concerned for Connor's
OL,12,Fhealth and safety, Lindsay installed a
OL,13,Fcamera in Connor's flat.
OL,15,F"Within three days, we saw five
OL,16,Fmembers of staff neglecting and
OL,17,Fabusing him," said Lindsay.
