OL,6,F"They would mock him, they would vape
OL,7,Fnext to him, shout in his face, he
OL,8,Fdidn't have a drink for 14 hours, and
OL,9,Fhe's meant to drink regularly because
OL,10,Fof the effect the drugs he needs have
OL,11,Fon his kidneys."
OL,13,FShe watched as her son was left alone
OL,14,Fon multiple occasions for hours at a
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,FOn the night of January 10th 2024,
OL,18,Ffootage showed Connor alone, eating
OL,19,Ffrom a bin he had placed on his lap.
OL,20,FHe was eating out of it for almost an
OL,21,Fhour.
