OL,6,F"It hurts to watch it," Lindsay told
OL,7,Fme. "We had to take him to the GP to
OL,8,Fget a full check up because he
OL,9,Fcouldn't tell us what he had eaten.
OL,11,F"It was heartbreaking and it consumed
OL,12,Fmy life, because once I'd seen that, I
OL,13,Fcouldn't stop watching (the camera)."
OL,15,FOn several occasions, footage showed
OL,16,FConnor's carers fast asleep on
OL,17,FConnor's sofa in the middle of the day
OL,18,Fwhile he walks around the flat
OL,19,Funattended.
