OL,6,FConnor is seen speaking to his carer,
OL,7,Fclearly asking them something, but the
OL,8,Fcarer ignores him completely. One
OL,9,Fcarer is shown vaping next to Connor
OL,10,Fin his flat.
OL,12,F"When Lifeways first opened I thought
OL,13,FI could die happy, knowing he would be
OL,14,Fok but now I just think if anything
OL,15,Fhappened to me, what would happen to
OL,16,Fhim?," she explained.
OL,18,F"I'm not just doing this for Connor,
OL,19,Fit is happening to someone else's
OL,20,Fchild, someone else's brother or
OL,21,Fsister, and it needs to stop."
