OL,6,FThe last inspection of Lifeway's
OL,7,FCoventry home by the Care Quality
OL,8,FCommission, the independent regulator
OL,9,Fof health and social care in England,
OL,10,Fdowngraded the home from 'Good' to
OL,11,F'Requires Improvement', the
OL,12,Fregulator's second lowest rating.
OL,14,FITV News has also heard from several
OL,15,Fformer and current Lifeways staff
OL,16,Fmembers.
