OL,6,FMany said the homes they worked in
OL,7,Fwere constantly under-staffed, with
OL,8,Fworkers having no or very minimal
OL,9,Ftraining to provide personal care for
OL,10,Fpeople with complex mental and
OL,11,Fphysical needs.
OL,13,FSome said that they watched residents
OL,14,Fgain weight at an alarming rate in the
OL,15,Ftime they worked there, because they
OL,16,Fwere not taken out into the community
OL,17,Ffor exercise or given healthy meals.
OL,19,FOne whistleblower spoke to ITV News
OL,20,Fanonymously about her experience as a
OL,21,Fcare home manager for Lifeways.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/33
