OL,6,FStaffing levels, she claimed, were
OL,7,Fregularly below safe levels and
OL,8,F"dangerous" at weekends.
OL,10,F"You would get in so much trouble if
OL,11,Fyou booked agency workers, even if
OL,12,Fpeople called in sick," she told ITV
OL,13,FNews. "They were calling in sick
OL,14,Fbecause they were tired."
OL,16,F"The money from the local council was
OL,17,Fprobably going in Lifeways' pocket,
OL,18,Fbecause if we were receiving it we
OL,19,Fwould have been able to give (the
OL,20,Fresidents) a much better quality of
OL,21,Flife," the whistleblower told ITV News.
