OL,6,FAnalysis of data from the Care Quality
OL,7,FCommission by ITV News shows that
OL,8,Facross the 19 Lifeways services
OL,9,Finspected by the regulator in 2024,
OL,10,F63% were rated 'Requires Improvement'
OL,11,F(the second lowest rating).
