OL,15,Freceived 366 safeguarding alerts,
OL,16,Fsafeguarding concerns or other
OL,17,Fconcerns about Lifeways services in
OL,18,F2024. This is a 33% increase from
OL,19,F2023. Of the 366 received in 2024, 232
OL,20,Fwere safeguarding alerts or concerns.
