OL,6,FSteven Baskin is 47-years-old and has
OL,7,FDown's Syndrome. His father John
OL,8,Falways wanted to make sure Steven
OL,9,Fcould live as independently as
OL,10,Fpossible, supported with the care he
OL,11,Fneeded.
OL,13,FThe day I meet Steven, he greets me
OL,14,Fwith a beaming smile and welcomes us
OL,15,Fin the supported living home he lives
OL,16,Fin with full time carers in North
OL,17,FLondon.
OL,19,FHe takes me around the home,
OL,20,Fintroducing me to the staff and the
OL,21,Fhome's manager.
