OL,6,FHis father John, who is 80, visits
OL,7,FSteven every weekend. They go to the
OL,8,Fcinema and to restaurants, and on
OL,9,Foccasion to the West End to see a
OL,10,Fmusical, which is Steven's passion.
OL,12,FJohn is also Steven's advocate. For
OL,13,Fmany years the only suitable home he
OL,14,Fcould find for his son was 60 miles
OL,15,Faway in Northampton. Then in 2012 he
OL,16,Fmanaged to find Steven a supported
OL,17,Fliving apartment close to home in
OL,18,FNorth London, managed by Lifeways.
