OL,6,FJohn says by the time he removed
OL,7,FSteven from their care in 2020, his
OL,8,Fson was a shadow of the bubbly,
OL,9,Fconfident and happy man I met.
OL,11,FLike Connor, Steven was gaining
OL,12,Fsignificant amounts of weight.
OL,14,F"I was particularly worried about his
OL,15,Fhealth. He was getting fatter and
OL,16,Ffatter, he was unhappy," John told me.
OL,18,F"He wouldn't get out of bed. The state
OL,19,Fof the flat was terrible. Rotting
OL,20,Ffood, filthy and dirty. There was a
OL,21,Flack of soap for him to wash."
