OL,6,FIn 2019 Steven became unwell and was
OL,7,Fadmitted to hospital for treatment.
OL,8,FJohn went to see him, and during the
OL,9,Fvisit Steven took his socks off. One
OL,10,Fof his feet had turned black.
OL,12,F"I was absolutely shocked. I called
OL,13,Fthe hospital staff and they were
OL,14,Fshocked as well. Nobody at Lifeways
OL,15,Fhad thought to remark on it or notify
OL,16,Fanyone," John told me.
OL,18,F"I was really horrified, because it
OL,19,Flooked like he could lose a foot. It
OL,20,Fwasn't just a blister."
